name: JudgeDao
description: In the digital currency world, the cost of crime is too low But what I want to tell you is that justice will never be absent We set up this project to defend your rights and interests with legal weapons. These funds will be used to track the fraudulent project parties. We will hire the best lawyer team to sue those fraudulent project parties, and the fined funds will be returned to the injured users Assangedao is our first project on file.
